00:31:47,751 --> 00:31:49,083
He's right.

557
00:31:49,185 --> 00:31:51,185
It's funny, yeah? (LAUGHS)

558
00:31:51,288 --> 00:31:55,022
Like Charlie Chaplin. (LAUGHS)

559
00:31:55,124 --> 00:31:56,491
(MAN LAUGHS)

