00:32:05,534 --> 00:32:07,467
Let's go.

561
00:32:07,569 --> 00:32:09,569
(GAETANO SIGHS)

562
00:32:13,008 --> 00:32:14,308
(SIGHS)

563
00:32:14,410 --> 00:32:15,842
CALAMITA: He thinks he can

564
00:32:15,944 --> 00:32:17,344
